### IsaYoga API - Exemplos de Requisições
### Use com REST Client (VSCode) ou copie os curl commands

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### Criar um novo usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Silva",
  "email": "maria@example.com"
}

###

### Listar todos os usuários
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users

###

### Buscar um usuário específico (substitua {id} por um ID real)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

###

### Atualizar um usuário (substitua {id} por um ID real)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Silva Santos",
  "email": "maria.santos@example.com"
}

###

### Deletar um usuário (substitua {id} por um ID real)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

###

#######################################
### CURL Commands (Terminal)
#######################################

### Health Check
# curl http://localhost:8080/health

### Criar usuário
# curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"name":"João Silva","email":"joao@example.com"}'

### Listar usuários
# curl http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users

### Buscar usuário
# curl http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{id}

### Atualizar usuário
# curl -X PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{id} \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"name":"João Silva Santos","email":"joao.santos@example.com"}'

### Deletar usuário
# curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{id}

